<% case @resource.default_locale || I18n.locale
   when :en -%>
Dear <%= @resource.display_name %>,

You have requested a link to reset your password for the application "<%= @project_name %>".

Please click here:
<%= @url %>

If you do not wish to change or recover your password, you can ignore this email.

Your password will only be reset if you follow the link above and set a new password.

Yours sincerely,

The project team "<%= @project_name %>"
